1: Basic String Manipulations:

Indexing: print(abd[0])
Slicing: print(abd[0:2])
Concatenation: print(fname, " ", lname)
Repetition: print(fname*3)
2: Case Conversion:

Uppercase: print(abd.upper())
Lowercase: print(abd.lower())
Capitalize: print(abd.capitalize())
Title Case: print(abd.title())
Swap Case: print(abd.swapcase())

3: String Stripping:

Strip Characters: print(abd.strip('A'))
Strip Whitespace: print(abd.strip())
Centering: print(abd.center(20))
Zero Fill: print(abd.zfill(20))

4: Splitting and Joining:

Split by Delimiter: print(name.split('Dodia'))
Join with Delimiter: print('#'.join(abd))
5: Reverse String:

Reverse Entire String: print(abd[::-1])
6: Replace Substring:

Replace Substring: print(abd.replace("$", ""))
7: Sorting Characters:

Sort Characters: print(sorted(abd))
